Changes for version 0.9.15
-------------------------
	* CTAPI port setting fixed with multiple readers
	* duplicate CTAPI reader instances display removed
	* PIN retry counting fixed up for CTAPI
	* some corner case error situations handled better
	* warning when certificates are about to expire

Changes for version 0.9.14
-------------------------
	* fixed bug "carderror 0x64 0xA2" with CTAPI
	* add card command logging with --verbose option
	* fix CTAPI comms for SPR532 reader
	* fix release packaging for Windows and Mac

Changes for version 0.9.13
